  <p>From breaking headlines to in-depth analysis, InsightStream curates the most relevant and trustworthy news sources in one streamlined experience. Whether you're a casual reader or a professional researcher, InsightStream helps you stay informed with clarity and confidence.</p>

  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Smart Aggregation:</strong> Get news from multiple trusted outlets in real time.</li>
